casebody.data:
Degener, Respondent, v. Underwood et al., Appellants. (Superior Court of New York City, General Term. December 5, 1892.) Action by Frederick L. Degener against John T. Underwood and others.

Argued before Dugro and Gildersleeve, JJ.

James A. Hudson, for appellants. J. E. Ludden, for respondent. Dugro, J.

The order denying a motion to retax costs is affirmed, with $10 costs.
